description: Boy oh boy, Boynton Beach is lucky to have this truck roaming the streets. The Inca Mix is  bringing the best Peruvian fusion fare to Floridians, and the proof is in the Pepa Pork Sandwiches (Roasted Pork Shoulder, Tangy Onions, Crispy Sweet Potato, all on a Toasted Hoagie Roll). You can also find other delicious dishes, like their Cholo Beef Sandwich (Stir Fried Short Rib, Caramelized Onions, Soy Sauce, Tomato, Crispy Fries, Cilantro, Mayo, all on a tasty Toasted Bun), and Rey Fish Sandwich (Egg Battered Catfish, Lettuce, Tomato, Tangy Onions, all on a terrifically tasty toasted Bun), Ceviche, and so much more. If you think you need a Peruvian food fix, then The Inca Mix is the perfect truck for you!
name: The Inca Mix
